<section id="testing">
    <h2>The Tests Your Doctor Isn't Running</h2>

    <p>Standard diabetes screening misses the decade of damage. Here's what actually matters:</p>

    <h3>1. Fasting Insulin Test</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Optimal:</strong> &lt; 5 μIU/mL</li>
        <li><strong>Warning:</strong> 5-10 μIU/mL</li>
        <li><strong>Danger:</strong> &gt; 10 μIU/mL</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Glucose Tolerance Test WITH Insulin</h3>
    <p>Not just glucose - measure insulin response at 0, 30, 60, 120 minutes</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Reveals hyperinsulinemia years before diabetes</li>
        <li>Shows how much insulin your body needs to control glucose</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. HOMA-IR Score</h3>
    <p>Calculated from fasting glucose × fasting insulin ÷ 405</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Optimal:</strong> &lt; 1.0</li>
        <li><strong>Insulin resistant:</strong> &gt; 2.0</li>
    </ul>
</section>

